ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST in order to add to the Import Control List the steel products that are subject to provisional safeguardsfor the purpose of administering the tariff-rate quotas through the issuance of import permits. The use of import permits will assist in determining the volume of imports that may be imported surtax-free.
